&lt;div id=&#34;history-making-history&#34; class=&#34;section level3&#34;&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;History Making History&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;/center&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Only these six players in MLB history have ever reached the career milestone of at least 3,000 hits AND 500 home runs…only six. It is one of the rarest achievements in all of professional sports.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
